item.title: CVE-2021-38959|2024-08-04T01:51:20.831Z -- ibm -- spss%20statistics
item.description: IBM SPSS Statistics for Windows 24.0, 25.0, 26.0, 27.0, 27.0.1, and 28.0 could allow a local user to cause a denial of service by writing arbitrary files to admin protected directories on the system. IBM X-Force ID: 212046.

item.title: CVE-2022-43855|2024-08-03T13:40:06.581Z -- ibm -- spss%20statistics
item.description: IBM SPSS Statistics 26.0, 27.0.1, and 28.0 could allow a local user to create multiple files that could exhaust the file handles capacity and cause a denial of service. IBM X-Force ID: 230235.
